Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.95,0:00:20.22,OP TL,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:13959,20226}But the white ball and the blue court,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.22,0:00:26.02,OP TL,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:20226,26026}such simple things,\Nyet they give my life meaning
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.02,0:00:32.25,OP TL,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:26026,32259}They show me\Nwhere I'll be tomorrow
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.25,0:00:39.92,OP TL,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:32259,39926}They show me\Nwhere my dreams are
