Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.15,0:01:36.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:93159,96892}{\i1}Our story begins\Nin a small fishing town
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.89,0:01:39.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:96892,99959}{\i1}on the Miura Peninsula\Nin Kanagawa Prefecture.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.45,0:01:59.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:115459,119292}{\i1}The spring semester is just starting\Nat the local Tachibana High School,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.29,0:02:03.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:119292,123292}{\i1}and consequently, all school sports clubs\Nresume their activities in full swing.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.02,0:02:05.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:124026,125259}{\i1}With one exception…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.15,0:02:26.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:142159,146059}{\i1}This room, belonging to the volleyball club,\Nhas not been open even once for half a year.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.05,0:02:29.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:146059,149959}{\i1}It became infamous around the school\Nas the "Forbidden Room".
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.79,0:02:37.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:152792,157059}{\i1}Just a year ago, Tachibana High School's\NVolleyball Club could boast
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.05,0:02:39.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:157059,159726}{\i1}a talented coach\Nand many great achievements.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.72,0:02:44.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:159726,164492}{\i1}However, when the coach left school\Nfor personal reasons,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.49,0:02:47.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:164492,167359}{\i1}students of older classes,\Nincluding their captain,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.35,0:02:52.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:167359,172892}{\i1}tried to fill the void after him by putting\Npressure on the younger club members.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.89,0:02:54.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:172892,174892}{\i1}Soon thereafter,\Na tragedy occurred.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.35,0:03:06.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:183359,186892}{\i1}One of the club members met\Nwith an early death due to harassment.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.89,0:03:09.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:186892,189326}{\i1}Her death was described\Nby the media of the whole country.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.32,0:03:12.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:189326,192326}{\i1}The club was closed soon after.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.89,0:03:19.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:196892,199559}{\i1}Better to forget about\Nthat accident as soon as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.55,0:03:23.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:199559,203692}{\i1}Everyone has the right to play with the ball.\NI have to rebuild this club.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.69,0:03:27.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:203692,207692}{\i1}This is how I want to spend\Nmy last year in high school.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.65,0:03:58.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:236659,238926}Mimi. Mimi!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.92,0:04:00.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:238926,240259}Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.25,0:04:01.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:240259,241692}Yukari?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.69,0:04:04.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:241692,244326}Oh boy, look at this mess.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.32,0:04:06.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:244326,246292}Come on, Yukari, we'll clean up.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.29,0:04:07.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:246292,247892}It can wait.\NYou'd better look here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.89,0:04:09.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:247892,249392}What's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.39,0:04:10.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:249392,250226}Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.22,0:04:12.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:250226,252726}They all want to join our club.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.72,0:04:15.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:252726,255192}Really? That many?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.19,0:04:18.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:255192,258092}Yes. Sixteen girls in total.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.09,0:04:22.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:258092,262326}Including you and me, our amazing club\Nwill already have eighteen members!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.32,0:04:23.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:262326,263859}That's a nice start.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.85,0:04:27.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:263859,267159}Awesome. Looks like\Nit'll go easier than I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.15,0:04:30.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:267159,270059}Girls, I'm Hijiri Mimi\Nfrom the third grade.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.05,0:04:31.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:270059,271092}Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.09,0:04:33.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:271092,273392}The pleasure is ours!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.89,0:04:40.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:277892,280059}You've opened\Nthe Forbidden Room?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.05,0:04:43.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:280059,283492}The Forbidden Room?\NWhat is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.49,0:04:45.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:283492,285559}Oh? Haven't heard of it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.55,0:04:48.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:285559,288792}So you probably also haven't heard that\Nthe room behind you is said to be haunted?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.89,0:04:51.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:289892,291759}Haunted?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.52,0:04:54.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:292526,294826}That's nonsense!\NWhat are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.82,0:04:58.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:294826,298792}Last summer, a schoolgirl died there\Nas a result of harassment by her team.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.79,0:05:00.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:298792,300559}I'm not making this up.\NIt was in the newspapers.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.55,0:05:03.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:300559,303092}So this is where\Nthat accident happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.09,0:05:04.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:303092,304459}So this is the club…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.69,0:05:08.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:305692,308926}You have quite unique hobby\Nif you want to train with ghosts.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.92,0:05:13.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:308926,313092}Girls, I'm Shiraki Rumi, captain of\Nthe Women's Basketball Club.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.09,0:05:18.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:313092,318426}Everyone who wants to enjoy\Nhealthy sports is welcome to join us.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.55,0:05:25.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:321559,325492}Don't let her fool you.\NShe's telling you that only to recruit you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.49,0:05:28.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:325492,328492}You know very well that there is\Nno such thing as ghosts.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.49,0:05:31.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:328492,331192}You came here to join\Nthe volleyball club, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.19,0:05:34.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:331192,334959}So don't listen to her\Nand help me clean this room.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.72,0:05:47.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:345726,347959}It's finally over.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.95,0:05:49.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:347959,349792}Time to rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.79,0:05:51.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:349792,351759}Oh? Where is everybody?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.75,0:05:53.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:351759,353792}They ran away.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.79,0:05:55.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:353792,355959}Ran away? Where to?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.95,0:06:00.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:355959,360159}What does it matter? What matters\Nis that they believed in that ghost story.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.15,0:06:02.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:360159,362326}What? You don't say!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.32,0:06:03.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:362326,363626}How many remained?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.95,0:06:06.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:363959,366026}I'm curious myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.02,0:06:12.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:369026,372026}One… Two… Three… Four.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.12,0:06:15.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:374126,375759}Just six…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.75,0:06:20.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:375759,380926}In the end, our club\Nwill have only eight people.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.92,0:06:25.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:381926,385192}No worries.\NIt's plenty enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.19,0:06:30.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:385192,390259}We just have to show that our club is cool,\Nthen more people will come in no time.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.25,0:06:31.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:390259,391859}Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.82,0:06:43.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:402826,403826}Yukari.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.82,0:06:46.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:403826,406092}Mimi, you won't believe it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.09,0:06:47.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:406092,407326}What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.22,0:06:51.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:408226,411092}This morning, three girls resigned.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.09,0:06:53.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:411092,413726}What are you talking about?!\NSo we only have five left?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.35,0:06:56.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:414359,416992}Something tells me that\Nit won't stop there and more will go away.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.55,0:07:01.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:417559,421926}All because of those stories about\Nthe Forbidden Room and ghosts.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.05,0:07:09.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:426059,429126}So we're the only two left?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.12,0:07:10.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:429126,430659}So it appears.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.65,0:07:12.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:430659,432659}No, there are three of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.99,0:07:16.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:434992,436326}Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.32,0:07:18.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:436326,438392}I'm Nishi Sumi'e from Class 1C.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.39,0:07:21.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:438392,441926}I was in a volleyball club\Nin junior high school.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.92,0:07:23.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:441926,443892}Really? That's great!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.89,0:07:27.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:443892,447659}What position did you play?\NAttacker? Setter?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.65,0:07:29.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:447659,449559}None of those things.\NI was a manager.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.55,0:07:30.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:449559,450759}A manager?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.75,0:07:35.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:450759,455059}Yes. That's why with me around,\Nyou won't have to worry about anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.99,0:07:39.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:455992,459126}Here, help yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.55,0:07:43.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:461559,463226}Please join our club!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.22,0:07:45.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:463226,465892}Volleyball is fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.19,0:07:49.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:466192,469126}We have a friendly atmosphere.\NCome and join us!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.12,0:07:51.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:469126,471592}We don't have any ghosts!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.59,0:07:54.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:471592,474592}At least no one has seen any yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.19,0:07:57.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:475192,477059}Don't say that,\Nit has the opposite effect.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.32,0:07:59.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:478326,479759}Oops.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.75,0:08:01.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:479759,481292}Hey, girls. Are you still looking?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.85,0:08:05.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:481859,485159}Oh, what could the chairman\Nof the Student Council want from us?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.15,0:08:09.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:485159,489626}The principal asked me\Nto call your captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.62,0:08:11.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:489626,491292}The principal wants to see me?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.29,0:08:17.29,Sign,(sign),0,0,0,,{TIME:491292,497292}{\an2}Storage space for boys' bicycles
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.59,0:08:20.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:497592,500992}Hey, you're the one who keeps\Nleaving their bike here?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.99,0:08:22.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:500992,502392}Why, you have a problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.39,0:08:27.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:502392,507326}That's my spot.\NIt's the closest to the gate.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.32,0:08:29.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:507326,509626}That's why I'm leaving it here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.62,0:08:32.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:509626,512659}Shut up.\NThis is a place for boys!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.65,0:08:34.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:512659,514292}Are you a boy?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.29,0:08:35.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:514292,515792}What, do I look like one to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.79,0:08:37.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:515792,517626}Don't talk back to me here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.62,0:08:43.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:517626,523426}You know that the students living near school\Naren't allowed to come by bicycle.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.42,0:08:47.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:523426,527159}That's right, Ichijō-kun. I'm sorry,\Nbut he's right. These are the rules.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.25,0:08:50.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:528259,530492}From what I remember,\Nyou moved here in January.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.49,0:08:56.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:530492,536459}So you haven't had the opportunity to learn\Nabout the council's rules on using bicycles.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.75,0:08:58.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:536759,538126}I know them.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.12,0:09:02.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:538126,542726}You cannot come by bicycle unless\Nyou live more than three kilometers away.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.72,0:09:06.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:542726,546459}You can also have a special permit,\Nbut you must send an application to get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.45,0:09:09.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:546459,549926}So you knew? And you still…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.32,0:09:16.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:551326,556459}Look at you. A textbook in the right hand,\Nand Student Council regulations in the left.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.45,0:09:18.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:556459,558459}Go whine to your teacher, nerd.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.19,0:09:22.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:559192,562059}I see that you've got\Nan uncivil tongue, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.05,0:09:24.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:562059,564359}I just want to ride my bike.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.89,0:09:27.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:564892,567559}Then why don't you just\Nsend the application?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.55,0:09:29.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:567559,569692}The rules are there to be broken.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.45,0:09:39.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:578459,579559}See you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.85,0:09:43.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:579859,583192}Wait a moment! Don't think\Nthat you can get away with it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.19,0:09:44.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:583192,584626}Calm down, Arashi.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.62,0:09:48.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:584626,588026}You're not going to fight with a girl, are you?\NYour black belt would be sad.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.05,0:09:54.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:593059,594326}Excuse me, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.32,0:09:55.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:594326,595192}Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.75,0:09:59.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:597759,599392}I heard that you called me, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.75,0:10:01.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:599759,601159}Ah, it's you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.15,0:10:02.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:601159,602859}How are things going with the club?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.19,0:10:05.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:603192,605626}Oh, perfectly well, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.62,0:10:07.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:605626,607326}Don't lie to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.82,0:10:10.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:607826,610692}You only have three people.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.42,0:10:14.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:611426,614692}I know that this is partly due\Nto that accident from last year.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.69,0:10:21.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:614692,621192}However, the Student Council will never\Nlet you start a club with only three people.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.19,0:10:22.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:621192,622359}Excuse me?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.99,0:10:28.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:622992,628259}I expect the final decision will be made\Nat the meeting in three days.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.25,0:10:33.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:628259,633092}Hijiri-kun. I understand that you try very hard,\Nbut you have to look at it from our perspective.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.09,0:10:34.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:633092,634959}Please wait, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.95,0:10:38.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:634959,638359}I promise to find new members\Nbefore the council meeting.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.35,0:10:41.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:638359,641959}You must have at least\Nsix people to play volleyball.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.45,0:10:46.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:642459,646992}I will find three more girls.\NI promise, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.99,0:10:49.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:646992,649126}I appreciate your effort.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.12,0:10:53.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:649126,653126}I just hope it doesn't end\Nin any accident, like it did the last year.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.19,0:11:13.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:672192,673759}Grandma, more!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.65,0:11:15.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:674659,675859}Yes, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.92,0:11:21.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:676926,681726}Mimi, something happened? Today we're having\Nyour favorite sukiyaki and you have no appetite.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.72,0:11:23.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:681726,683526}Somehow I don't feel\Nlike eating today.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.99,0:11:26.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:683992,686826}It's completely unlike you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.65,0:11:43.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:698659,703592}{\i1}Mom, Dad… What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.39,0:11:47.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:704392,707526}Grandma, look!\NI think she's crying?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.62,0:11:51.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:708626,711959}I'm not crying at all.\NThings are perfectly well.
Comment: 0,0:12:00.02,0:12:00.02,Default,[chapter],0,0,0,,{TIME:720026,720026}Part B
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.72,0:12:07.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:723726,727359}Everyone is welcome\Nto join our volleyball club!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.55,0:12:09.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:727559,729859}Don't hesitate, come and join us!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.52,0:12:12.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:730526,732559}Wait! Hiraki-san, Yamada-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.22,0:12:16.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:733226,736026}You were in the club last year.\NWhy don't you join us back?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.72,0:12:18.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:736726,738592}Please, come back.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.42,0:12:23.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:739426,743059}True, we love volleyball\Nand we like you, Hijiri-san…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.05,0:12:24.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:743059,744826}Then why don't you join?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.82,0:12:27.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:744826,747559}But that room is haunted.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.72,0:12:30.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:748726,750559}Do you really believe\Nin these rumors?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.99,0:12:33.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:750992,753492}You see, somebody\Nactually saw that ghost.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.49,0:12:37.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:753492,757059}Who's that?\NWho's spinning such tales?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.05,0:12:38.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:757059,758659}That would be me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.55,0:12:40.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:759559,760492}Shiraki-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.59,0:12:44.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:762592,764159}Did you really see a ghost there?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.35,0:12:46.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:764359,766626}Yes, from time to time.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.69,0:12:49.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:767692,769092}Do you have any evidence?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.65,0:12:52.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:769659,772059}And do you have evidence\Nthat it's not haunted?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.02,0:12:56.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:774026,776459}See? You can't deny it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.49,0:13:09.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:786492,789892}Hijiri-san, we would join\Nyour club if we could.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.89,0:13:11.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:789892,791626}I'm not lying.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.62,0:13:16.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:791626,796926}Thank you.\NIt's too early to give up.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.15,0:13:19.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:798159,799359}Think she'll be okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.35,0:13:20.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:799359,800659}Dunno.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.09,0:13:27.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:805092,807292}What are you trying to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.29,0:13:28.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:807292,808826}I'm going to sleep here today.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.82,0:13:29.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:808826,809792}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.25,0:13:31.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:810259,811926}Here? In the middle?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.92,0:13:34.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:811926,814326}Exactly.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.32,0:13:36.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:814326,816459}But why?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.82,0:13:40.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:816826,820326}We can't recruit anyone because\Nof these nonsense ghost stories.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.32,0:13:41.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:820326,821759}I've had enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.75,0:13:45.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:821759,825992}But somebody really died here.\NWhat if it's really haunted?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.42,0:13:47.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:826426,827959}Don't say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.99,0:14:03.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:839992,843326}{\i1}There is no such thing as ghosts.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.19,0:14:06.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:846192,846992}It can't be…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.32,0:14:18.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:856326,858726}Hijiri-san is so brave.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.72,0:14:23.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:858726,863826}When she sees that I brought her coffee,\Nshe'll cry with joy and fall into my arms.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.09,0:14:40.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:879092,880992}Who… Who are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.99,0:14:41.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:880992,881992}It's me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.99,0:14:44.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:881992,884126}It's a ghost!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.45,0:15:01.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:900459,901959}Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.92,0:15:05.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:903926,905526}Mimi, we have a problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.52,0:15:06.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:905526,906492}What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.75,0:15:11.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:907759,911959}The whole school's talking about a ghost that\Nshowed up in the Forbidden Room last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.95,0:15:13.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:911959,913326}What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.32,0:15:17.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:913326,917159}Apparently Arashi-kun saw it\Nwith his own eyes yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.59,0:15:20.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:917592,920626}Wait, that…\NThat was Arashi-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.19,0:15:25.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:921192,925326}It's getting worse and worse.\NYour idea only added fuel to the fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.59,0:15:26.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:925592,926559}You're right…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.72,0:15:29.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:926726,929026}Excuse me, is Hijiri-san\Nfrom the Volleyball Club here?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.02,0:15:30.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:929026,930192}That's me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.19,0:15:33.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:930192,933559}I'm Sekiya Kimiko from Class 1B\Nand I would like to join your club.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.19,0:15:37.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:935192,937626}You don't mind\Nthose ghost stories?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.85,0:15:42.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:937859,942492}Of course not. But if that room\Nis really haunted, I'd love to see a ghost live!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.12,0:15:46.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:944126,946226}Anyway, we're happy\Nto take you in.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.59,0:15:49.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:946592,949526}In return, I have a small request.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.52,0:15:51.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:949526,951892}I'll try to accommodate it if I can.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.89,0:15:56.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:951892,956492}Can I practice storytelling\Nbetween the games?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.49,0:15:58.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:956492,958526}Storytelling?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.52,0:16:03.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:958526,963992}I've always wanted to belong to a club\Nthat tells funny stories on a stage.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.99,0:16:06.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:963992,966926}This school doesn't\Nhave a club like that, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.92,0:16:10.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:966926,970159}Well, no problem. And what's\Nyour experience with volleyball?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.15,0:16:11.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:970159,971859}Ah, yes. None whatsoever.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.85,0:16:16.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:971859,976692}But when it comes to storytelling, I'm pretty good.\NYou'll be able to judge it yourself in a moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.25,0:16:21.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:979259,981126}Nice to welcome you all…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.12,0:16:23.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:981126,983159}Wait, we take your word for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.15,0:16:24.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:983159,984359}Oh, boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.95,0:16:27.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:986959,987892}Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.89,0:16:29.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:987892,989392}Who are you and\Nwhat are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.39,0:16:32.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:989392,992059}Uh, is it true that it's haunted?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.05,0:16:33.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:992059,993526}Even if it is, what then?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.52,0:16:36.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:993526,996259}If it really is,\NI'd like to join your club.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.39,0:16:40.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:997392,1000626}I might be a little big,\Nand I'm certainly not the strongest,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.62,0:16:44.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1000626,1004259}but I am fascinated\Nby everything paranormal.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.25,0:16:48.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1004259,1008092}If you really have ghosts here,\NI'd like to be part of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.09,0:16:50.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1008092,1010426}To be honest, it's— ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.42,0:16:52.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1010426,1012992}Sure, it's haunted! Welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.22,0:16:56.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1015226,1016759}We already have five.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.75,0:16:59.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1016759,1019559}Yes. We only need one more.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.55,0:17:01.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1019559,1021559}Thank you and have a nice day.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.75,0:17:08.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1026759,1028826}She needed a bicycle to shop.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.79,0:17:12.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1029792,1032626}I wonder how she\Nspends her free time.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.62,0:17:13.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1032626,1033826}I think she's hiding something.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.82,0:17:17.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1033826,1037326}It's better to stay away\Nfrom such people.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.42,0:17:31.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1048426,1051459}It's the first time\NI saw Ichijō-san smile.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.45,0:17:36.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1051459,1056659}Who is he and why did he\Ntalk to that gloomy girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.65,0:17:38.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1056659,1058226}Interesting, indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.82,0:17:41.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1060826,1061992}Hey, man.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.99,0:17:43.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1062992,1063992}Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.95,0:17:50.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1067959,1070792}Hi, Yukari.\NWhat are you looking at?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.79,0:17:52.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1070792,1072459}Look. Over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.89,0:17:56.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1073892,1076726}That's the guy from yesterday,\Nwho talked to Ichijō-san, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.72,0:17:59.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1076726,1079192}Who on earth is he?\NI'll go check!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.19,0:18:01.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1079192,1081292}Don't fool around, Yukari!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.29,0:18:06.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1081292,1086059}I want to know who he is.\NYou know, knowledge is power, and so on!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.52,0:18:10.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1087526,1090059}That's Yukari for you,\Nshe just has to know everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.75,0:18:13.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1090759,1093126}But that was a pretty good question.\NWho is he, indeed?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.95,0:18:20.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1096959,1100059}Hey, you! It's a parking lot for boys!\NCan't you read?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.75,0:18:23.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1101759,1103392}Alright, I'll show you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.82,0:18:31.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1108826,1111226}You stupid goose.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.92,0:18:51.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1129926,1131926}Well, now you've done it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.69,0:18:54.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1132692,1134759}Where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.95,0:18:58.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1135959,1138192}Not good.\NArashi's pissed off.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.19,0:18:59.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1138192,1139792}God help that girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.79,0:19:01.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1139792,1141492}Take your dirty hands off.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.49,0:19:03.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1141492,1143992}What… What did you say? Dirty?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.99,0:19:07.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1143992,1147692}Time for you to feel these dirty hands\Non your foul mouth!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.69,0:19:08.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1147692,1148526}No!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.52,0:19:09.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1148526,1149526}Hijiri-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.52,0:19:12.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1149526,1152359}Arashi-kun, what were you\Ntrying to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.35,0:19:16.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1152359,1156726}She keeps parking here illegally\Nand takes our spots!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.19,0:19:22.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1157192,1162026}Ichijō-san, you know he's right.\NWhy don't you ask the principal for a permit?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.02,0:19:24.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1162026,1164059}But what should\NI write as the reason?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.05,0:19:29.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1164059,1169926}I saw you using the bicycle to do shopping\Nafter school and help your family.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.92,0:19:32.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1169926,1172026}That's a very good reason.\NThey can't say no to that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.05,0:19:36.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1174059,1176059}See? Just write that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.05,0:19:39.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1176059,1179126}Hijiri-san, don't stick your nose\Nin where it's not welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.62,0:19:43.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1180626,1183359}I'm sorry.\NI didn't mean to.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.25,0:19:49.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1184259,1189492}If you're mingling with my affairs,\Nlet me mingle a bit with yours, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.49,0:19:50.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1189492,1190859}You want to create a club, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.79,0:19:54.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1192792,1194892}I can join your club.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.72,0:19:57.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1195726,1197359}For… For real?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.05,0:19:59.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1198059,1199792}Don't get too excited.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.79,0:20:01.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1199792,1201692}I'll join under one condition.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.69,0:20:03.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1201692,1203359}I want to be the captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.25,0:20:07.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1205259,1207092}So what will it be?\NDo we have a deal?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.62,0:20:11.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1208626,1211859}Or would you rather let the council\Nreject your application?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.85,0:20:13.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1211859,1213392}How's it gonna be?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.89,0:20:21.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1217892,1221959}Hijiri-san, don't agree.\NThis crazy girl is just trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.95,0:20:25.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1221959,1225759}Besides, she has no experience.\NIt's crazy to make her the captain.
