Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.99,0:21:53.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1310992,1313559}What is this attitude?\NAnd you want to be the captain?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.55,0:21:55.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1313559,1315592}I am the captain,\Nso I make the rules.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.59,0:21:59.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1315592,1319392}Ichijō-san, why did you set the condition\Nthat you wanted to be our captain?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.39,0:22:04.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1319392,1324759}Isn't that obvious? To do what I please.\NI hate to be ordered around.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.75,0:22:09.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1324759,1329292}We've barely managed to gather six people,\Nand everything is falling apart already.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.29,0:22:11.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1329292,1331826}What is waiting for us next?
